snippet.title: Waltair Veerayya Theatrical Trailer | Megastar Chiranjeevi | Ravi Teja | Shruti Haasan | Bobby | DSP
snippet.description:
Waltair Veerayya Theatrical Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers. Waltair Veerayya is an upcoming Telugu film ft. Megastar Chiranjeevi, Ravi Teja, Shruti Haasan and Catherine Tresa. Music composed by Rockstar Devi Sri Prasad. Story, Dialogues & Direction by KS Ravindra (Bobby Kolli). Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y Ravi Shankar under the banner Mythri Movie Makers, Audio On Sony Music.

Waltair Veerayya Grand Release on 13th January, 2023.

snippet.title: Veera Simha Reddy Trailer | Nandamuri Balakrishna | Gopichand Malineni | Thaman S | Shruti Haasan
snippet.description:
Veera Simha Reddy Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers. Presenting our NATASIMHAM Nandamuri Balakrishna, Shruti Haasan and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in Veera Simha Reddy. The film has been Written and Directed by Gopichand Malineni. Music composed by Thaman S. Cinematography helmed by Rishi Punjabi. Dialogues Penned by Sai Madhav Burra and Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y Ravi Shankar, under the banner Mythri Movie Makers.

Veera Simha Reddy Grand Release on 12th January, 2023.

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. snippet.title: Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song | Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare | Ajaneesh Loknath |Nithin Krishnamurthy
snippet.description:
Kantara music director B. Ajaneesh Loknath comes with another magical creation in Nithin Krishnamurthy's directorial debut, Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare. The first single "Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song" sung by the Music director himself and penned by Yogarajbhat Fans is an another attraction for the film. Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare is a one-of-a-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy's hostel, featuring 500 new talents and cameo by superstars, Rishab Shetty, Ramya, Pavan Kumar & Shine Shetty.  The film is made under the Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. The director who has also served as one of the four producers of the film along with Prajwal B.P., Varun Kumar, and Arvind S. Kashyap, who is handling cinematography as well and Presented by Paramvah Pictures.

Listen to the song on all your favorite Music platforms : https://bfan.link/hostel-hudugaru-protest-song

https://bit.ly/SubscribeToA2Music for more !

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:

Being heartbroken is a very tough place to be in, but what if you meet the love of your life when you are in pieces? Will Maya be able to welcome Anand into her heart?

"Amma Anand Avakai" is a Telugu Romcom Web Series featuring Soniya Singh & Pavan Sidhu as leads.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3661 - Bawri Ne Kiya Bagha Se Breakup?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3661 - 6 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3661: A Heart-Broken Bagha!
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bawri does not arrive at Lovely Garden, Bagha goes to her apartment. Bagha is greeted by her neighbor as Bawri's fianc√©e, but she informs Bagha that Bawri has urgently left her place. Bagha reluctantly exits her apartment. A few moments later, Bagha receives a text message from Bawri in which she states that she will never speak to him again. Bagha is devastated, and Sodhi discovers him crossing the street erratically. What made Bawri decide to cut all ties with Bagha?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3661, 6 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Qalandar Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - Hiba Aziz - 7th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

snippet.description:
#pavbhaji #mumbaistyle #bhaji 

INGREIDENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

2 Onions (Slices)
3 Desi Tomatoes 
1 Capsicum
1 Whole Garlic 
2 Inch Ginger 
2 - 3 Tbsp Butter 
Oil As Needed 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder 
1 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
1 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 Beatroot 
1 - 2 Carrot 
1 Cup Peas
3 Potatoes 
250 - 300 Gms Cauli Flower 
1.5 Cups Water 
4 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Bleck Pepper Powder 
2 Tbsp Kasuri Methi 
 Coriander Leaves 

FOR TADKA 

3 - 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped )
1 Onion (Finely Chopped )
2 Tbsp Pav Bhaji Masala 

FOR PAV 

2 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Poav Bhaji Masala 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
Coriander Leaves.

Shraddha and Sankar have done almost everything to get control of the Pandey house. The seven-year-old shocking evil plan is about to be revealed. Will anyone ever know about their evil deeds?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 1 : Ek Se Bhali Do - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Duolingo and learn any language for free - https://app.adjust.net.in/jgl36j4

Ye life achche achchon ko halaal kar deti hain lekin hamare Rinku ki kahani thodi different hain. Isne khud ja ke musibat se panga liya. Rinku ki life mast chal rahi thi. Bade sheher mein sarkari naukari ki tayyari kar raha tha aur ek girlfriend bhi thi, Raveena, jo isse apna naukar samajhti thi Par phir bhi Rinku apne roommate Neetu ke sath khush tha. Phir iski life mein aayi Sangeeta aur life mein 5th gear lag gaya. Ek ke baad ek kamaal hone laga aur apna Rinku halaal hone laga. Yakeen na ho to khud dekh lo. Ek aisi kahani jis mein music hai, drama hai, action hai ( Rinku ki life mein ) , romance hai aur bahut saari confusion ke sath double dose of comedy bhi hai. Full family ke sath enjoy this special presentation

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3660 - 5 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3660: Bagha's Date 
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka shares some exciting news about the business deals of Gada Electronics, which makes Jethalal very happy. Jethalal gets impressed with his employees' performances and gifts them brand-new phones. Bagha notices Jethalal's happy mood and decides to ask for the day off to go on a date with Bawri. Jetha grants Bagha a day off, and he is off to meet Bawri. Is Bawri excited about Bagha as well? She has some news to share with Bagha; what does she have to say to him?¬†

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3660, 5 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. ROASTED KASURI METHI POWDER | ‡§≠‡•Å‡§®‡•Ä ‡§π‡•Å‡§à ‡§ï‡§∏‡•Ç‡§∞‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•á‡§•‡•Ä ‡§™‡§æ‡§â‡§°‡§∞ A PINCH

FRESH CORIANDER | ‡§π‡§∞‡§æ ‡§ß‡§®‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ AS REQUIRED (CHOPPED)
Method:
Add all the ingredients of the paste into a mixer grinder jar & grind it into a fine paste, make sure you soak the cashews in boiling water for 10-15 minutes before adding it, you can also boil it for 5 minutes.
To saut√© the paneer, set a pan over high heat & once it gets hot, add the oil & butter.
Once the oil gets hot, add the cubed paneer, salt & kashmiri red chilli powder, then toss the paneer over high flame for 1-2 minutes, doing this step will help the paneer to hold its structure in the gravy, once sauteed remove the paneer into a bowl & set it aside until you make the gravy.
To make the gravy, heat a wok or a kadhai then add oil & butter, once the oil gets hot, add all the whole spices along with, garlic & chopped green chilli, stir well & then add the onions & cook over medium high flame until the onions turn light golden brown.
Once the onions turn light golden brown add turmeric powder & kashmiri red chilli powder, stir well & then add a splash of hot water, stir well & cook the masala for 2-3 minutes.
Further add the prepared paste along with salt & sugar, stir well & cook over medium high flame until the oil separates.
Once the oil separates add hot water as required to adjust the gravy then cook for 2-3 minutes, then taste the gravy & adjust the seasoning accordingly.
Further add the paneer, butter & all the remaining ingredients, stir well & cook only for 1-2 minutes & then finally sprinkle some more fresh coriander.
Your paneer butter masala is ready, serve hot with naan, tandoori roti or rumali roti.

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 704 - 6 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 704: Online Daaku
--------------------------------------------
Vinay makes a phone call to his teacher, namely, John. John arrives at the police station and tells Maddam Sir that Vinay is innocent and someone else is trying to copy his app design to defraud people. Meanwhile, Pushpa Ji arrives at the police station. She whines about some dacoits in Chambal who have stolen all her wealth. Karishma Singh and Pushpa Ji go on a sting operation to investigate Rohan's true identity. They discover intriguing facts about Rohan. The confusion of being the brains of such a crime between two Rohans and Vinay happens. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 704, 6 Jan 2023
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences add to the drama madam and comedy.

‚ñ∫*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye‚Ä¶ parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha.
